videoDetails.title: Plane Crash
videoDetails.shortDescription: In a TV first, Discovery Channel remote control crashes a 727 plane into the dessert...all in the name of science. With cameras and crash test dummies on board, leading experts attempt to capture a plane crash as it unfolds to help improve airline safety.
videoDetails.author: discoveryfulleps
